{"hash":"078fc6d6e8b85aa861762ea8eddb610306c07883","data":{"markdownPage":{"id":"7e7a03f0cfcd76d4517aadc9bab58e8a","title":"Linux基本开发环境配置git,c++,nodejs,nginx","description":"","path":"/linux/linux-git-c-nodejs-nginx/","timeToRead":1,"content":"<h2 id=\"linux基本开发环境配置gitcnodejsnginx\"><a href=\"#linux%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEgitcnodejsnginx\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Linux基本开发环境配置git,c++,nodejs,nginx</h2>\n<p>前一篇文章配置了基本的SSH，本文来讲讲关于基本的开发环境的配置，包括git，c，c++，nodejs，nginx。</p>\n<h3 id=\"安装git和配置无密码登录github\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85git%E5%92%8C%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%97%A0%E5%AF%86%E7%A0%81%E7%99%BB%E5%BD%95github\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>安装git和配置无密码登录github</h3>\n<pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">yum install git\n\nssh-keygen -t rsa -C &quot;github_id_email&quot;\nGitHub上，打开“Account settings”--“SSH Keys”页面，\n然后点击“Add SSH Key”，填上Title（随意写），\n在Key文本框里粘贴 id_rsa.pub文件里的全部内容。\n\nssh -T git@github.com\ngit config --global user.name &quot;github_name&quot;\ngit config --global user.email &quot;github_id_email&quot; \n\n下载个github项目试试\ngit clone git@github.com:cicdops/cicdops.git</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"安装c和c的编译开发环境\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85c%E5%92%8Cc%E7%9A%84%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>安装c和c++的编译开发环境</h3>\n<p>这个group的打包安装还是第一次用，赞一个！</p>\n<pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">dnf install gcc\ndnf groupinstall &quot;Development Tools&quot;</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"安装nodejs\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85nodejs\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>安装nodejs</h3>\n<p>作为最流行的变成环境，真的是低头不见抬头见，迟早都得装，所以现在就搞定她。</p>\n<pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">yum install nodejs\n安装的gridsome模块玩玩把。\nnpm install --global --force @gridsome/cli</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"安装nginx\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85nginx\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>安装nginx</h3>\n<pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">安装nginx\ndnf install nginx\n/bin/systemctl start nginx.service\nfirewall-cmd --zone=public --add-port=80/tcp  --permanent\nsystemctl restart firewalld</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"配置终端支持中文\"><a href=\"#%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%BB%88%E7%AB%AF%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>配置终端支持中文</h3>\n<p>最后再来个重量级的配置，必不可少，有了这个才是完美的Linux开发环境。</p>\n<pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">localectl status\nlocalectl list-locales\ndnf install langpacks-zh_CN.noarch\nlocalectl set-locale LANG=zh_CN.utf8</code></pre>\n<p>如果你是使用putty来SSH的，那么还需要配置下。\n<img src=\"https://img2020.cnblogs.com/blog/46653/202004/46653-20200416202409680-267573013.png\" alt=\"putty\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"欢迎关注公众号：cicdops\"><a href=\"#%E6%AC%A2%E8%BF%8E%E5%85%B3%E6%B3%A8%E5%85%AC%E4%BC%97%E5%8F%B7%EF%BC%9Acicdops\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>欢迎关注公众号：cicdops</h2>\n<p><img src=\"http://aishizhe.cn/cicdops/gzh12.jpg\" alt=\"devops9\"></p>\n","sidebar":"","next":"","prev":"","headings":[{"depth":2,"value":"Linux基本开发环境配置git,c++,nodejs,nginx","anchor":"#linux基本开发环境配置gitcnodejsnginx"},{"depth":3,"value":"安装git和配置无密码登录github","anchor":"#安装git和配置无密码登录github"},{"depth":3,"value":"安装c和c++的编译开发环境","anchor":"#安装c和c的编译开发环境"},{"depth":3,"value":"安装nodejs","anchor":"#安装nodejs"},{"depth":3,"value":"安装nginx","anchor":"#安装nginx"},{"depth":3,"value":"配置终端支持中文","anchor":"#配置终端支持中文"},{"depth":2,"value":"欢迎关注公众号：cicdops","anchor":"#欢迎关注公众号：cicdops"}]},"allMarkdownPage":{"edges":[{"node":{"path":"/linux/linux-git-c-nodejs-nginx/","title":"Linux基本开发环境配置git,c++,nodejs,nginx"}},{"node":{"path":"/linux/linux-centos8-ssh/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/devops/all/","title":"DevOps"}},{"node":{"path":"/devops/dev-ops-jobs/","title":"为什么需要DevOps"}},{"node":{"path":"/devops/dev-ops-skill/","title":""}},{"node":{"path":"/devops/","title":"什么是 cicd，devops"}},{"node":{"path":"/devops/dev-ops-summary/","title":"什么是 cicd，devops"}},{"node":{"path":"/devops/dev-ops-tools/","title":""}}]}},"context":{}}